flowchart TB
    main["main<br/>Primary integration branch<br/>for non-breaking development"]
    rel10["release/1.0<br/>Stable maintenance branch<br/>for 1.0.x patch releases"]
    rel20["release/2.0<br/>Integration branch<br/>for breaking changes planned for 2.0"]

    nb["feature/* or fix/*<br/>Non-breaking work branches from main"]
    br["breaking/*<br/>Breaking work branches from release/2.0"]

    nb -->|PR to main| main
    br -->|PR to release/2.0| rel20

    main -. maintenance line .-> rel10

    main --> sync["Sync workflow:<br/>runs weekly and can also be triggered manually<br/>to check whether main can be merged into release/2.0"]
    sync --> conflicts{"Merge conflict detected?"}
    conflicts -->|No| auto_pr["Workflow automatically creates a PR<br/>from main to release/2.0"]
    conflicts -->|Yes| manual_pr["Resolve conflicts manually<br/>and create the PR manually"]
    auto_pr -->|Merge PR| rel20
    manual_pr -->|Merge PR after resolution| rel20